query: WITH entities AS (SELECT status, email, id FROM customers WHERE ((status = ANY($1)) AND (COALESCE((email, id) < ($4, $3), $3 IS NULL))) ORDER BY email DESC, id DESC LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: CustomerId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.email desc, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
